<p><iframe src="/ninth-bb/html/3d2355dd7a7d8d7c2306d121caaa684c300eab5a-822703850610562833" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div style="background-image: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/aiad-homescreen/blue_squares_2.gif); background-repeat: repeat;">
<p><br /></p>
<div style="center no-repeat ; float: center; border: solid 2px #000000; margin: 10px 40px 0px 40px; border-radius: 8px;">
<div style="margin: auto; text-align: center; width: 600px; padding: 2px 2px 2px 2px; color: black; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; opacity: .6;">

<p><strong>我是Dr.Ninth的私人助手，IOTA.aic。</strong><br />
<strong>这里是Dr.Ninth的人事档案，请输入您想查询的信息。</strong></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/ninth-bb/IOTA.aic" width="75px" alt="IOTA.aic" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<br />
<br />
<br /></div>
<br />
